<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id784f72b4-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s582a–7"><num value="582a–7">§ 582a–7.</num><heading> “State” defined</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The term “State” as used in this subchapter shall include Puerto Rico, the Virgin Islands, and Guam.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id784f72b5-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/87/788/s8">Pub. L. 87–788, § 8</ref>, <date date="1962-10-10">Oct. 10, 1962</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/76/807">76 Stat. 807</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/92/318/tV/s506/j">Pub. L. 92–318, title V, § 506(j)</ref>, <date date="1972-06-23">June 23, 1972</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/86/351">86 Stat. 351</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="id784f72b6-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id784f72b7-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id784f72b8-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1972—<ref href="/us/pl/92/318">Pub. L. 92–318</ref> inserted reference to Virgin Islands and Guam.</p>
</note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="statutoryNotes" id="id784f72b9-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Statutory Notes and Related Subsidiaries</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="effectiveDateOfAmendment" id="id784f72ba-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Effective Date of 1972 Amendment</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Amendment by <ref href="/us/pl/92/318">Pub. L. 92–318</ref> effective after <date date="1970-06-30">June 30, 1970</date>, see <ref href="/us/pl/92/318/s506/n">section 506(n) of Pub. L. 92–318</ref>, set out as an Effective Date note under <ref href="/us/usc/t7/s326a">section 326a of Title 7</ref>, Agriculture.</p>
</note>
</notes>
